                    <img src="~/css/Images/danceactivities.jpg" alt="Youth Programmes">
                    <div class="news-content">
                        <h3>Youth Programmes</h3>
                        <p>Our youth programme provides life skills and extra-mural activities through dance and cultural workshops, helping children with homework and engaging in dialogue on various topics that affect them</strong>.</p>
                        @* <a href="#" class="btn-more">Click for more →</a> *@
                    </div>
                </article>
                <br />
                <article class="news-card urgent">
                    <h3>Homework and Reading Programme!</h3>
                    <p>The homework and reading programme is aimed at improving the young people’s literacy skills and enhancing learning at the school.</p>
                    @* <a href="#" class="btn-more">Full Story →</a> *@
                </article>

            </aside>
